name: JUNGLE GOD
description:
You have Summoned the Jungle God.

Elusive in a prehistoric landscape, the shadows conceal your wanderings. Those who do not believe in your existence are doomed, those who know of you dare not mutter your name in fear of what evil comes with you. The silence within the Jungle in your presence takes the breathe away from your victims. 

You are now a God in this domain.
